{"tid":1298184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] 示威者旗_09_07_19","createTime":"2019-07-08T20:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T16:44:47.000Z","uid":138446,"like":112,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"04c16ac5a663749f3e2de2c4dbbe47c7dea0a9b9","tid":1298184,"uid":138446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43YxAff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43YxAff.jpg&h=f0c11031&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7GnXtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg7GnXtB.jpg&h=ecc908f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mbv0J8B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMbv0J8B.jpg&h=5986035c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5TSnc1W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5TSnc1W.jpg&h=a6c66719&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫定設計，大家再比意見。<br />\n(英文係比國際媒體登報用既，簡潔易明少字為本)<br />\n<br />\n建議加個大聲公，可以一路講。<br />\n例如：<br />\n呢度係香港人既呼籲，前方警務人員請出示委任證。<br />\nHere is Hong Kong citizen's announcement to all police force, please show your warrant card.<br />\n(有禮貌D搶下鏡頭，又講下英文禁，到佢地打過泥個畫面，佢地就會失民意，加上仲係有好多淺藍係唔知佢地無帶證)<br />\n<br />\n作用：<br />\n1:為左令後排更了解前線情況，用作溝通之用，要走都快D知要走。( 藍旗 )<br />\n2:國際媒體登報 ( 黃旗，黑旗 )<br />\n3:人人手機都可以整張有需要時用。( 紅旗 )<br />\n<br />\n**呢個post 主打文宣，要討論實際戰略請自行開post ，隨便拎圖隨便分享。<br />\n<br />\n感謝大家一晚參與。"},{"pid":"e7fb9623f8512d2952449a0113687a29909e6c8f","tid":1298184,"uid":276791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:31:17.000Z","msg":"港女買like KOL食人血饅頭消費社運賣廣告 被朋友痛斥後發爛渣兼自認做爛市<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297887</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ae6c56e7343f22ce68d8a1214ea62bbd0d45aa89","tid":1298184,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:31:20.000Z"